jishoData.meaning: sign of the hare or rabbit, fourth sign of Chinese zodiac, 5-7AM, east

onyomiExamples.meaning: the Rabbit (fourth sign of the Chinese zodiac), the Hare, hour of the Rabbit (around 6am, 5-7am, or 6-8am), east, second month in the lunar calendar

Earth Rabbit (16th term of the sexagenary cycle, e.g. 1939, 1999, 2059)
